name: What is Love? #3
description:
The answer of Artificial Intelligence to this eternal question is in this series of 10 generative NFTs (all editions of 10). This is the 3rd one.

Those who collect them all (or 10 editions in total) will be gifted 1 edition of the infinite video loop version of "What is Love?", which will be minted at the end of the series (also in an edition of 10. You can see a preview on Barabeke's Twitter).
